title: Create a Decentraland Committee in Phx Crypto
body: This proposal is to create a separate & independent Decentraland Committee in the Phoenix Crypto community. The DCL Committee will oversee the minting of Phoenix Crypto branded wearables, establishing a community presence in the metaverse and hosting events in Decentraland.
author: 0xBd13eA41066ed16d075B86B3082b3369814a1012
